ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A brief, natural language description of the intended semantics of the dynamic value.

ivardefs.name: expression
ivardefs.desc: An expression specifying the value of the customized element.

ivardefs.name: language
ivardefs.desc: The media type of the language for the expression.

ivardefs.name: path
ivardefs.desc: The path to the element to be customized. This is the path on the resource that will hold the result of the calculation defined by the expression.
